      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification evidence demonstrates correct implementation of governing equations at required level.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests on canonical Couette and Poiseuille flows confirm second-order spatial accuracy. Manufactured solution verification completed for the hemolysis transport scalar equation."
