      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) reported and discretization error bounded within acceptable limits for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh refinement study conducted on the FDA centrifugal pump geometry. GCI < 4% for hemolysis index and pressure rise across all operating points. Richardson extrapolation applied."
    },
    {
