      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions are documented and sufficiently representative of the simulation boundary conditions.",
      "rationale": "FDA round-robin experimental data used; test conditions (fluid viscosity, density, flow rates 2.5–7.5 L/min, rotational speeds 2500–3500 RPM) are well-documented and align with CFD boundary conditions."
    },
