      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric reported between simulation outputs and experimental measurements.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) predictions agree with experimental measurements within 15% across all tested operating points. Pressure-flow curves match within measurement uncertainty bands. Exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
